description: 2004 Corvette Z06Only 31K miles! Tastefully but mildly modifiedMillennium Yellow!If you’re looking for a pure, no-nonsense driver’s car, this is it. The 2004 Z06 represents the final year of the C5 Z06 and one of the most analog, raw performance Corvettes ever built. No turbos, no gimmicks—just a high-revving LS6, a 6-speed manual, and a chassis that talks to you every second you’re behind the wheel.Finished in iconic Millennium Yellow over black leather, this example has just over 31k miles and has been well maintained, garage kept, and carefully upgraded to enhance the driving experience without compromising its character.Performance & Upgrades Cold Air Intake – improved throttle response and induction sound Long Tube Headers – adds power and that unmistakable Z06 growl BC Racing Adjustable Coilover Suspension – tight, planted, and tunable for street or spirited driving Paint Corrected & Ceramic Coated – deep gloss and long-lasting protectionRecent ServiceFresh oil changeBrand new tiresFull inspection completedWhy the C5 Z06 MattersThe C5 Z06 is already a modern classic—and the 2004 model year is especially desirable as the last of the truly analog, lightweight, high-revving Z06s before electronics and refinement softened the edge. The LS6 is legendary for its reliability and character, and the driving experience is raw, mechanical, and engaging in a way newer cars simply can’t replicate.This car delivers:Unfiltered steering feelMassive grip and balanceA motor that begs to be revvedA connected, visceral driving experience every time you get inFuture CollectibilityLow-mile, clean, well-kept C5 Z06s—especially in standout colors like Millennium Yellow—are becoming harder to find. As enthusiasts continue to seek out cars with real driver involvement, the 2004 Z06 stands out as one of the last truly analog American performance icons and one that will continue to appreciate in value as years pass by. description: You’re looking at an incredibly special modern Chevrolet collectible—our like-new, 1,133 original mile 2004 Chevrolet Monte Carlo SS Supercharged, finished in stunning Victory Red with Ebony leather interior, built as a Dale Earnhardt Jr. Signature Series car and documented as #1596 of only 2,883 produced. This is the desirable factory supercharged SS model, powered by GM’s legendary 3.8L L67 V6 with Eaton M90 supercharger, paired with a smooth 4-speed automatic transmission, delivering that unmistakable factory-blown performance with everyday drivability. This Monte Carlo is loaded with options, including the power moonroof and the Dale Earnhardt Jr. package, and it presents exactly the way you’d expect a true 1,133-mile time capsule to—tight, clean, and beautifully preserved. Even better, it comes with a clean, accident-free Carfax history and the complete collector package: original window sticker, books, keys, remotes, and original floor mats—the kind of full documentation that almost never stays together, especially on cars with mileage this low. While there’s no official registry that can tell us exactly how many remain with miles anywhere near this, examples like this simply don’t surface often. This is top-of-the-food-chain territory for a Supercharged DEJ Signature Series—an outstanding opportunity for the collector who wants originality, documentation, and ultra-low miles all in one package. For more information on this gem, contact Kevin at Mashburn Motors. Visit Mashburn Motors online at www.mashburnmotor.com to see more pictures of this vehicle or call us at 586-468-6600 today to schedule your test drive.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2014 Dodge Challenger R/T. This powerful muscle car boasts a commanding presence on the road, combining the iconic Challenger styling with a thrilling performance that's sure to ignite your senses.

Highlighted features include:
• Shaker Package
• Super Track Pak
• 276 Watt Amplifier
• MOPAR Shaker Hood and Intake
• Painted Fuel Filler Door
• Rear Black Spoiler
• Shaker Graphics and Underhood Decal
• Black Instrument Panel Bezel
• Bright Pedals
• Dash Plaque
• Performance Steering Wheel
• Heated Front Seats
• 20" Aluminum Wheels
• 3.92 Rear Axle Ratio

Beneath the sculpted hood, you'll find the legendary 5.7L HEMI V8 engine, delivering an exhilarating 375 horsepower and 410 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a smooth-shifting 5-speed automatic transmission, this Challenger R/T offers a thrilling driving experience that will leave you craving the open road.

The Shaker Package takes the performance and style to the next level, with the iconic MOPAR Shaker hood scoop and intake system that not only looks incredible but also enhances airflow for improved power delivery. The Super Track Pak further elevates the driving dynamics, with a sport-tuned suspension, high-performance brakes, and a limited-slip differential for exceptional handling and control.

Inside, the Challenger R/T pampers you with premium features, including the Uconnect 730N navigation system, a powerful 368-watt amplifier, and a 40GB hard drive with 20GB of available storage. The heated front seats and leather-wrapped steering wheel add a touch of luxury, while the Boston Acoustic sound system delivers an immersive audio experience.

Whether you're seeking the ultimate muscle car thrill or a stylish and capable daily driver, this 2014 Dodge Challenger R/T is a remarkable choice. With its striking good looks, exhilarating performance, and impressive list of features, it's sure to captivate your senses and leave a lasting impression. We invite you to experience the power and presence of this exceptional vehicle firsthand. Schedule a test drive today and discover the true essence of the Challenger R/T.

description: This 2014 Chevrolet Camaro SS Coupe with the 1SS package is a true driver s car in every sense. Finished in Red Hot, it makes a bold first impression, made even more aggressive by the Black Rally Stripe Package that underscores its muscle-bound stance and performance DNA. At the heart of the experience is the legendary 6.2L V8, paired with a manual transmission that puts full control in the driver s hands. The 3.45 rear axle ratio sharpens throttle response, while the performance short-throw shifter delivers crisp, mechanical gear changes that make every shift feel deliberate and rewarding. Inside, the cabin keeps things focused and authentic with black sport cloth seating and a driver-oriented layout. Modern convenience is blended in seamlessly with the 7-inch touchscreen navigation system, while the Rear Vision Package including rearview camera and rear park assist adds confidence when maneuvering without dulling the car s raw edge. The power sunroof opens the cabin to the sound of the V8, turning every drive into an event. This Camaro SS isn t just about straight-line power it s about connection, sound, and control. With a manual gearbox and classic SS attitude, it delivers the kind of engaging, old-school muscle car experience that s becoming harder and harder to find.

Whether you're looking to conquer the open road or simply turn heads on the street, this 2017 Chevrolet Camaro 2LT is the perfect choice. description:
Introducing the exceptional 2017 Lexus RC 350, a true masterpiece of automotive engineering and design. This captivating coupe boasts a striking silver exterior that commands attention wherever it goes, complemented by a sleek and sophisticated silhouette that exudes confidence and style.

Under the hood, the RC 350 is powered by a potent 3.5L V6 DOHC Dual VVT-i 24V engine, mated to an 8-Speed Automatic with Direct Shift transmission, delivering an exhilarating driving experience with a remarkable blend of power and efficiency. Enjoy an impressive 19 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway, making this Lexus a truly versatile and practical choice.

• Navigation System with Mark Levinson Premium Audio
• 10 Speakers
• Air Conditioning with Dual-Zone Automatic Control
• Power Driver's Seat
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel with Paddle Shifters
• Blind Spot Monitor with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert
• Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
• 19-Inch F Sport Alloy Wheels

The Lexus RC 350 F Sport Package takes this coupe to the next level, with a host of performance-enhancing features that will thrill the senses. Enjoy the precision of the Adaptive Variable Suspension, the responsiveness of the Sport Vehicle Dynamics Integrated Management (VDIM) system, and the confident grip of the summer tires. The F Sport-exclusive front fender badges, unique grille, and aluminum sport pedals add a touch of aggressive style that is sure to turn heads.

Step inside the RC 350 and you'll be greeted by a cabin that exudes luxury and attention to detail. The power-adjustable front seats with driver's seat memory ensure a personalized and comfortable driving experience, while the LFA-inspired TFT instrumentation and Lexus Enform technology keep you connected and informed. The Nuluxe seat trim, heated and ventilated front seats, and premium audio system create an environment of refined sophistication.

Whether you're seeking a dynamic driving experience, a stylish and head-turning coupe, or a luxurious and well-appointed daily driver, the 2017 Lexus RC 350 is the perfect choice. We invite you to visit our showroom and experience the exceptional craftsmanship and performance of this remarkable vehicle for yourself. Let us demonstrate how the RC 350 can elevate your driving experience and enhance your lifestyle.

description:
Discover the thrilling performance and bold style of the 2017 Chevrolet Camaro 1LT. This sleek coupe is the perfect blend of power, sophistication, and cutting-edge technology, making it the ideal choice for the discerning driver.

Boasting a 3.6L V6 DI engine and an 8-speed automatic transmission, the Camaro 1LT delivers an exhilarating driving experience with 335 horsepower and 284 lb-ft of torque. Paired with rear-wheel drive, this Camaro offers exceptional handling and responsiveness, allowing you to conquer the road with confidence.

• REDLINE EDITION
• RS PACKAGE
• 3.6L V6 w/VVT

The Camaro 1LT's striking exterior is further enhanced by the RS Package, which includes 20-inch 5-split spoke premium Gray-painted, machined-face aluminum wheels, high-intensity discharge headlamps, LED taillamps, and a decklid-mounted lip spoiler. The Redline Edition adds a touch of sporty flair with black front and rear bowtie emblems, a Camaro emblem, a red accent grille, and 20-inch Black-painted aluminum wheels with red accents.

Inside, you'll find a premium audio system with Chevrolet MyLink, allowing you to seamlessly integrate your smartphone and access your favorite music, navigation, and more. The Camaro 1LT also boasts a host of advanced safety features, including a rearview camera, ABS brakes, and a comprehensive airbag system, ensuring your peace of mind on every journey.

With its exceptional performance, bold styling, and cutting-edge technology, the 2017 Chevrolet Camaro 1LT is the ultimate expression of automotive passion. Experience the thrill of the open road and make this Camaro your own. Visit our showroom today and let us help you discover the true power of this iconic sports car.

description: Rev up your engines and hit the road in style with this sleek Silver 2017 Ford Mustang! Whether you're looking for a daily driver or a weekend cruiser, this Mustang is ready to hit the road with you.Take the Next Step Toward Mustang OwnershipAre you ready to make the 2002 Ford Mustang GT Deluxe Coupe yours? This 2002 Chevrolet Monte Carlo SS is a true driver's car, blending dynamic performance with an array of premium features. With its low mileage and well-maintained condition, this vehicle represents an exceptional value in the pre-owned market. Visit our showroom today to experience the power and refinement of this remarkable sports coupe for yourself.

description: Get ready to rev up your engine and hit the road in style with this 2009 Honda Accord Coupe! This sleek and sporty white coupe is powered by a 2.4L DOHC MPFI 16-valve i-VTEC I4 engine, making every drive a thrill. With Active Noise Cancellation (ANC) and a smooth Drive-by-wire throttle, you'll experience a quiet and responsive ride every time you step on the gas.Equipped with a 5-speed automatic transmission and front wheel drive, this Accord Coupe offers a seamless and enjoyable driving experience. The double wishbone front suspension and independent multi-link rear suspension provide a comfortable and stable ride, while the variable pwr rack & pinion steering ensures effortless maneuverability.Step inside the cabin and relax in the luxurious leather-trimmed heated front bucket seats, complete with multiple power adjustments for the ultimate comfort. The 270-watt premium AM/FM stereo with a 6-disc in-dash CD changer and subwoofer will keep you entertained on the go, while the dual-zone automatic climate control keeps the interior at the perfect temperature.Safety is a top priority in this Accord Coupe, with features such as the Advanced Compatibility Engineering (ACE) body structure, dual-chamber front side airbags, side curtain airbags, and a tire pressure monitoring system to keep you protected on every journey. Plus, the 4-wheel anti-lock brake system with electronic brake distribution ensures precise stopping power when you need it most.But that's not all - this Honda Accord Coupe also comes with a Pwr moonroof, Xenon headlights, and chrome exhaust finisher for a touch of style. And with the availability of a Carfax report, you can purchase with confidence knowing the vehicle's history is transparent.So why wait? Experience the thrill of driving this 2009 Honda Accord Coupe today and make every drive an adventure!

description: 2011 Dodge Challenger R/T — HEMI 5.7L V8 (372 hp/401 lb-ft) Excellent overall condition • Clean CARFAX • Below 76,000 miles (average <5,000 miles/year) Overview This 2011 Dodge Challenger R/T is powered by the factory HEMI 5.7L V8 rated at 372 horsepower and 401 lb-ft of torque. It presents in excellent overall condition with a clean CARFAX history and very low mileage for its model year. The Challenger R/T pairs classic muscle-car styling with a straightforward equipment list built around performance and driver-focused ergonomics. Factory standard and commonly included features Performance and driveline - HEMI 5.7L V8 engine (372 hp/401 lb-ft) with factory-tuned power delivery and dual exhaust. - Rear-wheel drive configuration for traditional muscle-car handling balance. - Factory transmission as equipped from the factory (manual or automatic configurations were available from the factory). - Limited-slip rear differential available from the factory on many R/T builds to improve traction. - Heavy-duty cooling and drivetrain components matched to the V8. - Performance-oriented suspension tuning with independent front suspension and multi-link rear setup for a balance of comfort and control. - Four-wheel ventilated disc brakes with standard anti-lock braking system (ABS). Exterior - Iconic Challenger coupe profile with long hood and short deck proportions and R/T badging. - Factory paint finish and body trim consistent with original equipment. - Dual exhaust with visible outlets integrated into the rear valance. - Factory alloy wheels with performance tires (wheel size varies by build). - Power-adjustable side mirrors and standard exterior lighting with halogen headlamps (factory appearance and lighting packages were available). Interior and comfort - Five-passenger seating (two front bucket seats and a rear 60/40 split bench). - Supportive front seats designed for long-distance comfort and spirited driving, upholstery typically cloth in standard form with leather or heated leather available as factory options. - Full instrumentation cluster with speedometer, tachometer, fuel and temperature gauges and trip/odometer functions. - Tilt-and-telescoping steering column and steering-wheel-mounted audio and cruise controls on equipped models. - Manual or power-adjustable driver seat depending on factory options. Convenience and technology - AM/FM audio system with CD player and auxiliary input, factory infotainment options included the Uconnect system and available Bluetooth hands-free phone and media streaming on equipped vehicles. - Remote keyless entry and power windows/door locks as standard conveniences. - Cruise control and adjustable interior convenience features consistent with factory equipment levels. - Available options at the factory could include upgraded audio, satellite radio (SiriusXM), navigation, and additional comfort features. Climate and storage - Air conditioning with factory climate controls, automatic climate control was an available option on certain trims/packages. - Ample front and rear storage and sensible cabin layout for a two-door coupe. Safety - Front airbags plus side-impact thorax airbags and side-curtain airbags for outboard passengers (factory-installed supplemental restraint system). - Antilock brakes (ABS), traction control and electronic stability control were included to assist in maintaining control under varying road conditions. - Tire pressure monitoring system (TPMS) and standard restraint systems. Condition and documentation - This specific Challenger R/T has below 76,000 miles, averaging under 5,000 miles per year, and is described as being in excellent overall condition. - Clean CARFAX report with no reported major incidents. If you would like specific details about this vehicle’s original factory options, factory-installed transmission, wheel size, interior trim, or a copy of the CARFAX, those can be provided upon request.

Dressed to impress in a sleek, black exterior, this Mustang commands attention at every turn, embodying the classic allure and modern sophistication that only a Mustang can offer. The cabin is thoughtfully designed to provide both comfort and control, ensuring that every journey is as enjoyable as the destination. The interior’s clean lines and ergonomic layout create an ambiance that is both sporty and refined, making it the perfect setting for those who appreciate style and substance. Under the hood, the Mustang EcoBoost houses a formidable EcoBoost 2.3L Turbo I4 engine, delivering an exhilarating 310 horsepower and an impressive 350 ft. lbs. of torque. This powerhouse of an engine is engineered to provide a dynamic driving experience, offering the perfect balance of performance and efficiency. Whether you're cruising down the highway or navigating city streets, the Mustang's responsive powertrain ensures that you’re always in command. Paired with a cutting-edge 10-Speed Shiftable Automatic transmission, the Mustang EcoBoost offers seamless gear transitions that enhance both performance and fuel economy. This advanced transmission adapts to your driving style, providing smooth acceleration and precise control, allowing you to experience the road like never before. The 2019 Ford Mustang EcoBoost doesn’t just promise performance—it delivers accolades. Recognized as Edmunds's Buyers Most Wanted Sports Car, this Mustang is a favorite among enthusiasts and casual drivers alike. It has also been awarded the J.D. Power and Associates's Vehicle Dependability Study (VDS) Highest Ranked, a testament to its outstanding reliability and quality. These prestigious accolades underscore the Mustang’s reputation for excellence and make it a smart choice for those seeking a vehicle that combines style, performance, and dependability. Driving the Mustang EcoBoost is not just about getting from point A to point B, it's about the journey, the thrill, and the experience. This vehicle invites you to embrace the spirit of adventure, offering a ride that is as exhilarating as it is refined. The Mustang's legendary status is built on a foundation of innovation and performance, making it a timeless icon that continues to set the standard for sports cars. In conclusion, the 2019 Ford Mustang EcoBoost is more than just a car, it's a statement. It’s a declaration of your passion for driving and your appreciation for quality and performance. With its striking black-on-black aesthetic, powerful engine, and award-winning dependability, this Mustang is ready to elevate your driving experience to new heights. Don’t miss your chance to own a piece of automotive history—experience the thrill of the Mustang EcoBoost today and take the wheel of a legend.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with the exceptional 2025 Audi RS 6 Avant performance 4.0T quattro. This exhilarating sports wagon combines the power and precision of Audi engineering with the versatility and style you demand.

Standout features include:
• Bang & Olufsen Advanced 3D Sound System with 3D Sound
• Head-Up Display
• Heated Rear Seats
• Power Soft-Closing Doors
• Adaptive Cruise Assist with Lane Guidance
• Black Exterior Mirror Housings
• Black Exterior Trim
• Audi Side Assist with Pre Sense Rear
• Intersection Assist
• Remote Park Assist Plus
• Black Roof Rails
• Wheels: 22" Bi-Color Finish 5-Y-Spoke Design

Under the hood, this RS 6 Avant performance is powered by a potent 4.0L V8 Turbocharged engine that delivers an exhilarating 621 horsepower. Paired with Audi's legendary quattro all-wheel drive system, it provides unparalleled performance and handling, allowing you to conquer the road with confidence.

The striking Daytona Gray Pearl Effect exterior sets this vehicle apart, while the spacious and well-appointed cabin offers the perfect blend of comfort, technology, and style. From the luxurious Valcona leather seating to the advanced Audi MMI Navigation Plus system, every detail has been thoughtfully designed to enhance your driving experience.

Safety is also a top priority, with a comprehensive suite of driver assistance features, including Adaptive Cruise Assist, Intersection Assist, and Audi Side Assist with Pre Sense Rear, ensuring you and your passengers arrive at your destination with peace of mind.

Whether you're seeking the ultimate performance wagon or a versatile daily driver, the 2025 Audi RS 6 Avant performance 4.0T quattro is the perfect choice. Experience the power, precision, and sophistication that only an Audi can deliver. We invite you to visit our showroom and take this exceptional vehicle for a test drive. Let us demonstrate how it can elevate your driving experience and exceed your expectations.

Step into the commanding presence of the 2023 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 RST, a used powerhouse that combines rugged capability with refined style. Its Ecotec3 5.3L V8 engine delivers robust performance, ensuring you have the power to tackle any task with ease. The sleek Glacier Blue Metallic exterior turns heads, while the 4D Crew Cab offers ample space for both passengers and cargo. Safety is paramount in the Silverado 1500 RST, featuring advanced systems such as Automatic Highbeams, Front Collision Mitigation, and Lane Departure Warning, providing peace of mind on every drive. The Lane Keeping Assist and Stability Control further enhance your driving confidence, making it an ideal choice for those who value security alongside performance. Inside, enjoy the convenience of a Heated Steering Wheel and Heated Front Seats, keeping you comfortable in all weather conditions. The Navigation System and WiFi Hotspot ensure you re always connected and on the right path, while the Remote Engine Start offers added convenience for busy lifestyles. With its blend of power, safety, and modern technology, the Chevrolet Silverado 1500 RST is the ultimate companion for those who demand more from their vehicle. Be sure to call or visit Stonebriar Chevrolet to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

description: RPM Garage is a specialty car dealership conveniently located off I-35E in Dallas, Texas. With over 100 cars in stock, and new inventory arriving every day, we offer a wide variety of quality vehicles to make your dreams come true. Make sure to stop by and check out our BRAND NEW 40,000 sq/ft warehouse and take your dream car home TODAY! LET US FINANCE YOUR DREAMS! CLICK HERE TO BEGIN! We are proud to offer you this 2012 Cadillac CTS-V Wagon 1,200hp Fully Built Engine w/ Many Upgrades for sale! If you're searching for a heavily modified wagon built to be driven at the limit, this 2012 Cadillac CTS-V Wagon is the one for you! Powered by a supercharged 6.2-liter LSA V8 engine mated to a six-speed automatic transmission, this machine originally produced 556 horsepower and 551 lb-ft of torque, which the rear wheels put to the pavement. This power plant is not as it left the factory, though. The fully built engine features a KPE Racing CNC-machined rotating assembly, a Kong Performance LSA TVS2650 supercharger with a billet supercharger lid, Frankenstein upgraded heads, a Texas Speed Level 3 boost camshaft upgrade kit, a Kong Performance ZPE 2.750” supercharger pulley, a Fore Innovations triple-pump fuel system, and several supporting upgrades work in tandem to take this wagon's performance capabilities to the next level. This CTS-V Wagon sits on black-finished 17” CCW Classic beadlocks wrapped in Mickey Thompson ET Street R tires and is wrapped in matte black, a dark hue that makes this car look even more menacing. The interior is no less special than the rest of the car. Heated and ventilated leather sport seats deliver optimal support and comfort to the driver and passenger, and features like selectable drive modes, multi-zone climate controls, wood grain interior trim pieces, a dash-mounted clock, and keyless ignition only heighten the overall cockpit experience. An infotainment system with Bluetooth, navigation, phone connectivity, AUX, and a backup camera completes the interior, putting every available digital convenience at your fingertips. This 2025 Volvo V60 Cross Country B5 Plus is a stunning and capable crossover that offers an exceptional driving experience. With its sleek and rugged design, advanced technology features, and impressive performance, this vehicle is the perfect choice for those seeking a versatile and refined mode of transportation.

Powered by a 2.0L I4 Turbocharged engine and paired with an Automatic with Geartronic transmission, this V60 Cross Country delivers a smooth and efficient ride, achieving an impressive 24 city/31 highway MPG. The standard All-Wheel Drive system ensures confident handling in a variety of road conditions, making this Volvo an ideal companion for your everyday adventures.

The V60 Cross Country boasts an impressive array of premium features, including a state-of-the-art navigation system, high-performance audio system, and a host of advanced safety technologies. The heated steering wheel, heated front seats, and leather seating surfaces add a touch of luxury and comfort to every journey.

Volvo's commitment to safety is evident in the V60 Cross Country, which is equipped with a comprehensive suite of airbags, including dual front, dual side, and a knee airbag. The low tire pressure warning system and electronic stability control further enhance the vehicle's safety and stability.

Designed with the discerning driver in mind, the V60 Cross Country offers a refined and sophisticated driving experience. The 19-inch 5-Double Spoke Diamond-Cut Alloy wheels, combined with the sleek and distinctive exterior design, give this Volvo a striking presence on the road.

Whether you're commuting to work, embarking on a road trip, or tackling the great outdoors, this 2025 Volvo V60 Cross Country B5 Plus is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect balance of style, performance, and safety that Volvo is renowned for. Visit our showroom today to take this exceptional vehicle for a test drive and discover why it's the ideal choice for your next automotive purchase.

description: Rugged capability meets modern refinement in this Subaru Certified Pre-Owned 2025 Subaru Outback Wilderness an adventure-ready SUV built to go farther while keeping you comfortable every mile of the journey. Backed by Subarus comprehensive Certified Pre-Owned inspection and extended warranty coverage, this Outback delivers near-new confidence with exceptional long-term value. Powered by Subarus turbocharged BOXER engine and legendary Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, the Wilderness is engineered for confident performance in rain, snow, dirt roads, and mountain passes while still offering smooth everyday drivability. The Wilderness trim stands out with its bold styling, increased ground clearance, and trail-ready design, but its equally impressive inside. A power moonroof fills the cabin with natural light and fresh air, creating an open, airy feel whether youre commuting through the city or cruising scenic backroads. The integrated navigation system keeps you confidently on course wherever your travels take you, while Reverse Automatic Braking adds an extra layer of safety and convenience when maneuvering in tight spaces. Durable interior materials, supportive seating, and generous cargo capacity make it easy to pack up gear, luggage, or weekend supplies without compromise. With outstanding visibility, advanced safety technology, and Subarus reputation for long-term reliability, this Certified Pre-Owned 2025 Outback Wilderness is the perfect balance of comfort and true off-road capability. Available now at Carter Subaru in Shoreline, its a smart choice for drivers who want a vehicle thats just as ready for daily life as it is for the next big adventure. Come shop at Carter Subaru Today!

Experience the Perfect Blend of Luxury and Versatility with the 2022 Audi A4 allroad 45 Premium Plus
Discover the 2022 Audi A4 allroad 45 Premium Plus, a vehicle designed for those who crave both sophistication and adventure. This Navarra Blue Metallic beauty offers a dynamic driving experience with its 2.0L 4-Cylinder TFSI engine, delivering impressive power and efficiency. The A4 allroad&apos,s quattro all-wheel drive system enhances traction and stability, making it an ideal companion for diverse terrains and weather conditions. Its elevated ground clearance and rugged 4D Wagon bodystyle offer the flexibility to tackle both urban and off-road environments with confidence.
Inside, the A4 allroad 45 Premium Plus boasts a meticulously crafted interior that exudes elegance and comfort. Premium materials and advanced technology, including a virtual cockpit and intuitive infotainment system, keep you connected and in control. For those who seek a vehicle that embodies both luxury and practicality, the 2022 Audi A4 allroad 45 Premium Plus is the perfect choice.

description: A Free CARFAX for this vehicle is available at schompsubaru.com, where you can view the vehicle history report, ownership history, and maintenance reports.Introducing the Subaru Impreza RS loaner vehicle, available at Schomp Subaru. This gently used car offers exceptional value and the benefits of a well-maintained vehicle. The Impreza RS has been meticulously cared for and exclusively driven by our service customers, ensuring it is in top condition and ready for its next owner.With lower mileage and updated features, choosing a loaner vehicle like the Impreza RS from Schomp Subaru means you get the perks of nearly new cars. This quality vehicle has undergone a thorough inspection process, providing you with peace of mind about its reliability and performance.The Impreza RS loaner vehicle features a hatchback/liftback/notchback body style with a sleek silver exterior color, adding a touch of elegance to its overall look. Safety features include standard ABS, front and rear seat-mounted side airbags, as well as roof-mounted side curtain airbags for added protection.Notable features of the Impreza RS include a Harman/Kardon entertainment system and EyeSight driver-assist technology. Inside, you'll find a comfortable and spacious interior with seating for five passengers, ensuring a pleasant driving experience for all occupants.Experience the transparent and hassle-free purchase process with Schomp Subaru's One Price. One Person. One Hour.® sales approach when you explore our inventory of loaner vehicles. Bring home a quality Subaru Impreza RS loaner vehicle at a great price and enjoy driving a reliable and well-equipped car that meets your needs.

description: Discover the 2022 Kia Soul LX: A Perfect Blend of Style, Efficiency, and Safety for the Modern Driver Seeking a Distinctive and Versatile Driving Experience. The 2022 Kia Soul LX, in its stunning Snow White Pearl finish, is the ideal companion for those who crave individuality and practicality. Its 2.0L I4 DOHC engine paired with a CVT transmission ensures a smooth and efficient ride, perfect for city commutes and weekend getaways. The 4D hatchback design offers ample cargo space, making it a versatile choice for drivers who need flexibility without compromising style. Safety is a priority with features like Automatic Headlights, Brake Assist, and a comprehensive airbag system, providing peace of mind on every journey. The Soul LX also includes advanced technology such as a Back-Up Camera and Bluetooth Connection, ensuring you re connected and in control at all times. Inside, the Kia Soul LX offers comfort with its Cloth Bucket Seats and intuitive Smart Device Integration, allowing you to seamlessly manage your music and calls. The adjustable steering wheel and Steering Wheel Audio Controls enhance your driving experience, making every trip enjoyable. For those who value a unique blend of style, efficiency, and safety, the 2022 Kia Soul LX stands out as a remarkable choice. Be sure to call or visit Camelback Hyundai Kia to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

description:
This 2022 Subaru Outback Wilderness comes in with 70,850 miles and is built for drivers who don’t like turning around when the pavement ends. It’s rugged, confident, and purpose-built for adventure, while still being comfortable enough to handle everyday life without feeling like a compromise.

On the road, the Outback Wilderness feels planted and sure-footed, with a suspension setup designed to handle rougher terrain without beating you up on the highway. When conditions get less than ideal—snow, dirt, gravel, or mud—this Subaru really shines, delivering the kind of confidence that encourages you to keep going instead of playing it safe.

Inside, the gray leather interior strikes a great balance between durability and comfort. It’s designed to handle active lifestyles while still feeling refined, with a layout that’s intuitive and driver-focused. Everything feels thoughtfully placed, making long drives and off-grid weekends equally enjoyable.

Later in the story, the look ties it all together. Crystal White Pearl gives this Outback a clean, sharp appearance that contrasts perfectly with the Wilderness trim’s aggressive styling cues. A clean, no-accident history adds extra peace of mind to a vehicle that’s already built with confidence in mind.

As an Archibald’s Certified vehicle, this Outback has passed a rigorous multi-point inspection, received full interior and exterior reconditioning, and comes with a 3-month or 3,000-mile limited warranty for added confidence. And when you buy from Archibald’s, you’re choosing an award-winning, family-owned dealership serving the Tri-Cities since 2001, known for top ratings and exceptional care. This Outback Wilderness isn’t just ready for adventure—it’s waiting for it.


A negotiable documentary service fee of $200.00 may apply to each purchase.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2022 Subaru Outback Touring XT. This versatile and well-equipped SUV is the perfect companion for your adventures, offering a seamless blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge technology.

Boasting a sleek White exterior, this Outback Touring XT is equipped with a host of premium features that will enhance your driving pleasure:

• Crystal White Pearl Body Side Molding
• Auto-Dimming Exterior Mirror with Approach Light
• Footwell Illumination Kit
• Splash Guards
• Rear Bumper Cover
• All-Weather Floor Liners
• Rear Seat Back Protector

Step inside and you'll be greeted by the stunning Nappa Leather-Trimmed Upholstery, providing unparalleled comfort and luxury. The 12-speaker harman/kardon® audio system and STARLINK 11.6" Multimedia Navigation System will keep you entertained and connected on every journey.

Powered by a 2.4L DOHC engine and Lineartronic CVT transmission, this Outback Touring XT delivers impressive performance with its Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system. Enjoy the confidence of 23 city/30 highway MPG, ensuring you can tackle any road with ease.

Additional standout features include a Power Moonroof, Power Liftgate, Heated and Ventilated Front Seats, Heated Rear Seats, and a Heated Steering Wheel, elevating your driving experience to new heights.

This 2022 Subaru Outback Touring XT is a true testament to Subaru's commitment to quality, safety, and innovation. With only 45,367 miles on the odometer, this vehicle is ready to take you on countless adventures, whether it's a weekend getaway or your daily commute.

Cascade Autocenter in Wenatchee, WA is your trusted Chevrolet and Subaru dealership, proudly serving North Central Washington since 1980. Family-owned and deeply rooted in our community, we're committed to delivering an exceptional automotive experience built on honesty, transparency, and care. Whether you're searching for a new Chevrolet or Subaru, a Certified Pre-Owned model, or a reliable used car or truck, our experienced sales team is here to help every step of the way. Explore our online inventory, schedule a test drive, or discover flexible financing and trade-in options that make upgrading easy and affordable. If you don't see the exact vehicle you want, our CarFinder tool will notify you as soon as it arrives. Visit Cascade Autocenter in Wenatchee on North Miller Street or call (509) 663-0011 to experience why local drivers have trusted our dealership for quality vehicles, expert service, and genuine community support for more than four decades.

description: ===== Used 2022 Subaru Outback Wilderness — Turbo Power & True Off-Road Capability =====This used 2022 Subaru Outback Wilderness is the most rugged Outback ever built, engineered for drivers who want real off-road capability without sacrificing everyday comfort. With a turbocharged engine, increased ground clearance, and trail-ready hardware, the Wilderness trim is purpose-built for adventure.*Clean title**Original MSRP:* $40,987==== Recent Service ====Recently serviced and inspected, including a completed pre-delivery inspection, 70,000-mile service, fresh oil and filter change, and a new engine air filter.==== Performance & Exterior ====Powered by a 2.4L turbocharged SUBARU BOXER® engine paired with a high-torque Lineartronic CVT, this Outback Wilderness delivers strong low-end power and confident traction. Features include Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, Dual X-Mode with Snow/Dirt and Deep Snow/Mud settings, off-road tuned suspension, Active Torque Vectoring, and an impressive 9.5 inches of ground clearance.Exterior highlights include 17-inch black alloy wheels with a full-size spare, LED headlights with high beam assist, LED fog lights, front skid plate, anti-glare hood decal, Wilderness exterior trim, and ladder-style roof rails rated for up to 700 lbs static load capacity.==== Interior Comfort & Convenience ====The Wilderness cabin features durable StarTex® water-repellent seating surfaces, a 10-way power driver’s seat with lumbar support, heated front and rear seats, heated mirrors, a windshield wiper de-icer, and dual-zone automatic climate control. Additional touches include all-weather floor mats with Wilderness logos, rear seat reminders, and a 60/40 split-folding rear seat for cargo flexibility.==== Technology & Connectivity ====Equipped with Subaru STARLINK® 11.6-inch Multimedia with navigation, this Outback supports Apple CarPlay®, Android Auto™, Bluetooth connectivity, SiriusXM®, multiple USB ports front and rear, wireless charging, an auto-dimming HomeLink® compass mirror, and over-the-air map updates.==== Safety & Driver Assistance ====Subaru EyeSight® Driver Assist Technology includes adaptive cruise control with lane centering, automatic emergency braking, lane departure and sway warning, blind spot detection with rear cross-traffic alert, a rear vision camera with guidelines, and a 180-degree front view monitor for added confidence on tight trails.==== Why Buy from Walser? ====At Walser, you’ll enjoy Upfront Pricing and a transparent, pressure-free buying experience. Every vehicle is carefully inspected so you can drive away confident, whether you’re commuting daily or heading deep into the backcountry.

Discover the perfect fusion of adventure and sophistication with this stunning 2023 Subaru Outback Touring. This exceptional vehicle is a true testament to Subaru's unwavering commitment to engineering excellence and unparalleled safety.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, this Outback Touring is equipped to elevate your driving experience:

• Leather Seats
• Backup Camera
• Navigation System
• Bluetooth
• Apple CarPlay
• Android Auto

Additionally, the Outback Touring comes equipped with the TECH PACKAGE 2, which includes a Wireless Charger, Auto-Dimming Exterior Mirror with Approach Light, and a Woodgrain Interior Trim Kit, further enhancing your comfort and convenience.

Powered by a 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with a CVT Lineartronic transmission, this Outback Touring delivers an exceptional balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 26 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway.

You'll also enjoy the peace of mind of Roadside Assistance, a $0 deductible, and a transferable warranty.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2023 Subaru Outback Touring. With its impressive capabilities, premium features, and Subaru's renowned safety and reliability, this vehicle is the perfect companion for your next adventure.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and versatility with the 2023 Kia Soul LX. This captivating compact crossover is ready to elevate your driving experience and transform the way you navigate the roads.

Boasting a striking Orange exterior, the 2023 Kia Soul LX is a true head-turner. Complemented by a host of impressive features, this vehicle is designed to cater to your every need. Explore the highlights:

• Envelope Cargo Net
• Carpeted Floor Mats

Beneath the sleek exterior, the 2023 Kia Soul LX is powered by a robust 2.0L I4 DOHC engine, delivering an exceptional balance of performance and fuel efficiency. With an impressive 29 city/35 highway MPG, you can enjoy the open road with confidence, knowing you'll spend less time at the pump.

Step inside the spacious cabin and experience the perfect blend of comfort and technology. The 6 Speakers, AM/FM/MP3/HD Audio System, and Apple CarPlay & Android Auto integration keep you connected and entertained on every journey. The Rear window defroster, Power windows, and Remote keyless entry add to the convenience, while the Traction control and 4-Wheel Disc Brakes with ABS ensure a smooth and safe ride.

For added peace of mind, the 2023 Kia Soul LX is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. Dual front impact airbags, Dual front side impact airbags, Overhead airbag, and Occupant sensing airbag work together to protect you and your loved ones. The Exterior Parking Camera Rear and Auto High-beam Headlights further enhance your driving confidence.

Whether you're navigating the city streets or embarking on a road trip, the 2023 Kia Soul LX is the perfect companion. With its versatile cargo space, Split folding rear seat, and Envelope Cargo Net, you can easily accommodate your lifestyle needs.

Experience the exceptional value and uncompromising quality of the 2023 Kia Soul LX. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can elevate your driving experience.

        Safety and Security
        • Active blind spot system - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you. An active blind spot system not only alerts you to the presence of a vehicle to your sides or rear but helps prevent you from making an unsafe lane change. Replace fear and uncertainty with the confidence and safety of the Active blind spot system.
        • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
        • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
        • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
        Technology and Telematics
        • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

description:
Discover the 2023 Subaru Impreza: A Crimson Red Pearl Hatchback for the Adventurous Spirit Seeking Performance and Safety in Every Drive
For those who crave the thrill of the open road, the 2023 Subaru Impreza delivers a driving experience that is both exhilarating and secure. With its 2.0L DOHC engine and CVT Lineartronic transmission, this used Impreza offers a seamless blend of power and efficiency that is perfect for navigating city streets or winding country roads. The all-wheel-drive system ensures you maintain control, no matter the weather or terrain, making it an ideal choice for those who value reliability and performance.
Safety is paramount in the Impreza, with features like automatic headlights, brake assist, and a comprehensive airbag system, including knee and rear head airbags, providing peace of mind for you and your passengers. The stability and traction control systems further enhance your confidence behind the wheel.
Inside, the Impreza&rsquor,s smart device integration and Bluetooth connection keep you connected and entertained, while the back-up camera and keyless entry add convenience to your daily routine. With its striking Crimson Red Pearl exterior and sporty rear spoiler, this 4D hatchback is as stylish as it is functional, making it a standout choice for drivers who demand more from their vehicle.
When you think auto, think Autova‌

Why Buy from Paragon Honda? When you choose this 2023 Subaru Outback Limited from Paragon Honda, you're not just buying a used car - you're investing in quality, reliability, and peace of mind. Located in Woodside, NY 11377, we're proud to offer the best selection of certified pre-owned Subaruvehicles and top-tier used cars in the Queens area. Here's why savvy buyers trust us: Transparent Pricing: At $24,300, what you see is what you pay Customer-First Service: Our award-winning team treats you like family, backed by an excellent customer satisfaction rating. Convenience: From complimentary pick-up and delivery for service and sales, to easy financing options, we make car buying stress-free. Also for your convenience: we have our service department open 24 hours a day and 7 days a week. One Owner! Power Moonroof and Heated Steering Wheel and Navigation System ($2,060 value)
  • DriverFocus (driver Monitoring System)
  • Heated Steering Wheel
  • Power Moonroof
  • Subaru STARLINK 11.6\' Multimedia Navigation System Radio
 POWER MOONROOF & HSW & NAVIGATION SYSTEM, SLATE BLACK, PERFORATED LEATHER-TRIMMED UPHOLSTERY Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Rear camera with washer - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. Even if there are sloppy conditions, the washer keeps the camera's view clean. Rear camera with washer is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe
Technology and Telematics
  • Wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
Ready to drive home this 2023 Subaru Outback Limited today at Paragon Honda in Queens NY? Call us at 718-550-1710 to schedule your visit. Don't miss out - at this price $24,300 it won't last long! The displayed Pre-Owned vehicles are in limited quantities, unique, and often one of a kind based on the specific vehicle's options, colors, and mileage. These vehicles are offered on a first come, first served basis and are subject to prior sale. It should be understood that the displayed vehicles are a sampling of what may be available, not every vehicle will be continuously available at all times for every consumer, and additional similar vehicles may be available but not yet posted. Due to the high demand for our individually selected vehicle inventory, there may be times when an individual vehicle is no longer available at the time you arrive at the dealership. This may occur due to a time delay between posting the vehicle, its actual sale and delivery, and its removal from the website. Posting, sale, and delivery of all pre-owned vehicles is an evolving process, and occasionally displayed vehicles may not be available for a variety of reasons, including prior sale, removal or transport to another location, or awaiting title and ownership confirmation. To better ensure a specific vehicle's availability, please contact the dealership to confirm its current status. Advertised pricing is valid for same-day delivery only and is subject to change without notice. Vehicles not purchased and delivered on the same day may be subject to repricing. Price includes everything except your local sales tax, registration, and $175 documentation fee.

description:
Our stylish Accident Free, One Owner 2023 Subaru Outback Onyx Edition AWD adds dark details to go with its dynamic capability in Magnetite Gray Metallic! Motivated by a 2.5 Liter BOXER 4 Cylinder that offers 182hp to a paddle-shifted Lineartronic CVT for athletic performance. This All Wheel Drive SUV also has exceptional traction with standard X-MODE, and it sees nearly 32mpg on the highway. LED headlights, LED fog lamps, black alloy wheels, roof rails, a hands-free liftgate, sunroof, and eye-catching Crystal Black Silica mirror caps help bring out the bold side of our Outback's design.

Ready for camping, commuting, carpooling, and more, our Onyx Edition cabin has heated StarTex water-repellent front seats, power-adjustability for the driver, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, and keyless access/ignition. Staying connected comes easy with an 11.6-inch touchscreen, full-color navigation, WiFi compatibility, wireless Android Auto/Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, and a six-speaker sound system. There's clever cargo space, too, with central and overhead consoles.

Subaru takes an intelligent approach to safety with a rearview camera, blind-spot monitoring, and EyeSight technologies such as emergency steering assistance, adaptive cruise control, automatic braking, lane-keeping assistance, and more. Get out in front of your busy days with our Outback Onyx Edition! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Park Chrysler Jeep Used Test Drive Towards Ownership!

description:
Welcome to Hyundai of Yakima, this used 2015 Toyota Venza XLE with only 95,587 miles is a standout choice for drivers in Yakima and Central Washington who want the right vehicle at the right price. At Hyundai of Yakima, we select vehicles that deliver real value, dependability, and everyday confidence. Hyundai of Yakima is the #1 source for buying pre-owned vehicles in Central Washington. Every used vehicle at Hyundai of Yakima goes through a thorough 152+ point inspection to ensure safety, performance, and peace of mind. Inventory is moving fast, let us help maximize your tax refund to help lower your monthly payments or lower the overall price of your next vehicle. This vehicle is a This Vehicle is Equipped with: Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.
Ready to schedule a test drive? Visit Hyundai of Yakima at 3204 Fruitvale Blvd Yakima WA 98902 or call us at (509) 248 1500. Why should you choose Hyundai of Yakima? -One Price, One Promise Guarantee No Haggling- Just our best Market-Based price, backed by our market value guarantee. -Complete Mechanical Inspection of Every Used Car Our thorough 150+ point inspection ensures every used car we sell is fit to sell our mother's. So, you'll have the confidence that you know what you are purchasing. -6 Month/6,000 mi No Bills for The Basic \'No Bills for the Basic\' Guarantee. We cover brakes, tires, bulbs, and wiper blades if they fail within the first 6 months or 6,000 miles. -7 day/500 mi Exchange Guarantee Not the right fit? Exchange it for something else- No questions asked. -72 Hour/250 mi Full Money Back Guarantee If for whatever reason you want your money back within 72 hours of purchase, we will give you a 100% refund, including taxes as long as you return the vehicle in the same condition that it was when you took delivery. Some restrictions apply. -No Hassle No Obligation Pre Approvals Get approved in under 30 minutes with a full credit report and explanation- No pressure, No cost. -Flexible Financing Options We partner with local credit unions and national banks to give you the best financing choices. Bienvenido a Nombre de tu concesionario - Aqui Todos Pueden Conducir! Aceptamos todo tipo de credito: Buen credito, Mal credito, ITIN, y compradores primerizos. Ofrecemos la mejor garantia en Yakima, con una garantia de 3 meses y 3,000 millas. Ademas, disfrute de tranquilidad con nuestro intercambio sin preguntas dentro de las 72 horas. Creemos en precios transparentes y honestos, y estamos comprometidos a ser impulsados por la comunidad. Visitenos hoy y salga conduciendo con confianza! The 2016 BMW 3 Series 4dr Sports Wgn 328d xDrive AWD is a masterful blend of elegance and performance, finished in an alluring Black Sapphire Metallic exterior. This vehicle exudes sophistication with its sleek lines and dynamic stance, making it a head-turner on any road. Under the hood lies a robust 2.0L 4-cylinder engine that ensures an exhilarating yet efficient driving experience. The all-wheel-drive system offers enhanced traction and stability, making it equipped to handle various driving conditions with ease.Inside, the cabin is adorned with premium Coral Red/Black Dakota leather upholstery, offering a striking contrast and a luxurious feel. The M Sport Package further accentuates the sporty essence with its distinctive elements and superior driving dynamics. With the Premium Package, occupants are treated to a range of comfort-enhancing amenities, ensuring a first-class experience on every journey. The state-of-the-art navigation system provides seamless guidance, keeping you on track whether navigating city streets or exploring new destinations.The Driver Assistance Package offers a suite of features designed to enhance safety and convenience, including advanced driver aids that elevate peace of mind. This wagon seamlessly combines practicality with luxury, providing ample cargo space without compromising on style or performance. The black interior complements the exterior perfectly, creating a unified and sophisticated aesthetic. Whether for daily commutes or weekend getaways, the 2016 BMW 328d xDrive AWD delivers in terms of both utility and driving pleasure. description:
Discover the perfect balance of efficiency, technology, and style in this 2016 Toyota Prius v Five. With its impressive fuel economy, advanced features, and sleek design, this hybrid marvel is the ideal choice for the eco-conscious driver seeking a spacious and versatile vehicle.

Boasting a remarkable 44 city/40 highway MPG, this Prius v Five delivers exceptional fuel efficiency, helping you save at the pump and reduce your environmental impact. Equipped with a 1.8L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V VVT-i Aluminum engine and a CVT transmission, this Prius v provides a smooth and responsive driving experience.

Key features include:
• Navigation System
• 6 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• CD player
• Radio data system
• Radio: Entune Premium Audio w/Navigation/App Suite
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic temperature control
• Power driver seat
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted A/C controls
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls

This Prius v Five also offers a host of advanced safety technologies, such as ABS brakes, Dual front impact airbags, Dual front side impact airbags, Knee airbag, Occupant sensing airbag, Overhead airbag, and Electronic Stability Control, ensuring your peace of mind on the road.

The exterior of this Prius v Five features a sleek, aerodynamic design in a stunning Silver color, complemented by 17-inch High-Gloss Alloy wheels and a rear spoiler for a touch of sporty elegance. The interior boasts a spacious and well-appointed cabin, with SofTex Seat Trim, Heated Front Bucket Seats, and a Rear Seat Center Armrest for maximum comfort and convenience.

Whether you're commuting, running errands, or embarking on a family adventure, this 2016 Toyota Prius v Five is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of efficiency, technology, and style – schedule a test drive today and discover the difference for yourself.

To determine the recall status of a vehicle, visit https://www.nhtsa.gov/recalls.*Another Mike Shaw One-Owner Vehicle, *Subaru Certified/7yr/100,000 miles, * No Accident History on CARFAX, *Extremely Clean and Well Maintained, *Complete Inspection Performed, *Huge Savings, *Subaru Eyesight Adaptive Cruise Control, *Local Trade In, harman/kardon® Speakers, Navigation System, Power Liftgate, Power moonroof. 26/32 City/Highway MPG Recent Arrival!Autumn Green Metallic 2024 Subaru Outback Touring AWD AWDSubaru Certified Pre-Owned Details:* Transferable Warranty* SiriusXM 3-Month trial subscription, $500 Owner Loyalty coupon & 1 year trial subscription to STARLINK* 152 Point Inspection* Powertrain Limited Warranty: 84 Month/100,000 Mile (whichever comes first) from original in-service date* Warranty Deductible: $0* Roadside Assistance* Vehicle HistoryThe 2024 Subaru Outback Touring is a premium midsize AWD SUV that blends comfort, capability, and technologymaking it an ideal choice for Colorado drivers who face diverse weather, rugged terrain, and everyday adventures. With advanced safety technology, a refined interior, and Subarus signature all-weather confidence, the Outback Touring delivers the versatility Colorado lifestyles demand. Whether you're navigating snowy mountain passes, commuting along the Front Range, or heading out for a weekend road trip, this model offers a balanced mix of performance, comfort, and practicality.Like all Outback's, the Touring comes standard with Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, providing enhanced traction and stability on snowy, icy, or wet roads ideal for Colorado's long winters and mountain passes. This system helps keep you in control whether you're climbing to ski resorts or cruising city streets.The Outback Touring stands out with Nappa leather-trimmed seats, ventilated front seats, and a heated steering wheel, delivering premium comfort for long drives across Colorado's scenic highways. The spacious cabin and thoughtful touches ensure a relaxed ride in all seasons.Equipped with an 11.6-inch Subaru STARLINK touchscreen with built-in navigation, wireless Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and a Wi-Fi hotspot, the Touring keeps you connected and entertained on every journey whether exploring mountain towns or navigating urban traffic.The 2024 Outback Touring includes Subarus trusted safety suite with features like EyeSight Driver Assist Technology, blind-spot monitoring, and reverse automatic braking helpful tools for busy Front Range highways, mountain roads, or winter weather conditions.The 2024 Subaru Outback Touring is an excellent choice for Colorado drivers seeking a premium AWD SUV that handles snowy conditions, mountain roads, and everyday life with confidence. Its all-season capability, advanced safety technology, refined interior comfort, and intuitive connectivity make it a versatile and dependable vehicle for Front Range commuters and outdoor adventurers alike. Whether you're heading to work, school, or the trailhead, the Outback Touring delivers the performance and peace of mind Colorado drivers value most.Mike Shaw Subaru in Greeley, CO treats the needs of each individual customer with paramount concern. We know that you have high expectations, and as a car dealer we enjoy the challenge of meeting and exceeding those standards each and every time. We proudly serve Denver, Boulder, Fort Collins, Longmont, Thornton, Aurora, Arvada, Commerce City, Parker, Johnstown, Westminster, Golden, Loveland, and Windsor. Allow us to demonstrate our commitment to excellence!

Welcome to Toyota Salinas . Our team strives to make your next vehicle purchase hassle free. We are honored at the opportunity to earn your business.

Vehicle Details
Discover exceptional value with this 2018 Volkswagen Golf SportWagen SE, located in Salinas, CA — the best-priced SportWagen available. This versatile wagon combines efficient performance and everyday practicality with a responsive 4-cylinder 1.8L gasoline engine and smooth front-wheel drive. Crisp handling and a fuel-sipping powertrain make it ideal for city commutes, coastal drives, and weekend getaways.

Inside, enjoy premium comfort with leather seats that elevate the cabin for driver and passengers. Stay connected and entertained on every trip: Hands Free Bluetooth and Android Auto deliver seamless smartphone integration, while a premium sound system and Satellite Radio provide rich audio for long drives. Thoughtful interior design offers ample cargo space and flexible seating to adapt to gear, groceries, or luggage with ease.

Safety and convenience features complement the SportWagen's refined ride, making it a smart choice for families, commuters, and adventure seekers. Meticulously maintained and inspected, this 2018 Volkswagen Golf SportWagen SE presents a rare opportunity to own a well-equipped, reliable vehicle at an unbeatable price in Salinas, CA.

Don't miss your chance to drive away in a premium compact wagon with modern connectivity, comfort, and the practicality Volkswagen is known for — all at the best price. Contact us to schedule a test drive and see why this SportWagen stands out from the rest.

This stunning SUV, dressed in a pristine white exterior, is not just a mode of transportation—it's a statement of style and reliability. Under the hood, the Outback boasts a robust 2.5L H4 engine, delivering a spirited 175 horsepower and 174 ft-lbs of torque. This powertrain, paired with a smooth 6-Speed Shiftable CVT, ensures that every drive is not only efficient but also exhilarating. Whether you're navigating city streets or exploring winding country roads, the Outback's responsive handling and impressive fuel economy make it the perfect companion for any journey. The attention to detail is evident in every stitch, offering a premium feel that elevates your driving experience to new heights. description:
Introducing the sleek and stylish 2009 Chevrolet HHR LT! This versatile and reliable vehicle is the perfect choice for anyone in the market for a compact car with plenty of room to spare. The LT trim level boasts a spacious interior with comfortable seating for up to five passengers, making it ideal for daily commutes or long road trips.

But don't let its compact size fool you, the 2009 HHR LT packs a punch when it comes to performance. With a 2.2L 4-cylinder engine, this car delivers a smooth and efficient ride, while also offering impressive fuel economy. Plus, with only 75,000 miles on the odometer, this vehicle is just getting started on its journey.

The exterior of the 2009 HHR LT is equally impressive, featuring a sleek silver metallic paint job and chrome accents that give it a modern and sophisticated look. The spacious cargo area is perfect for hauling groceries, sports equipment, or anything else you may need to transport.

But that's not all, this HHR LT comes equipped with a variety of convenient and high-tech features to enhance your driving experience. From power windows and locks to an AM/FM/CD stereo system, this car has it all. Plus, with extra spacing in the cabin, you and your passengers will have plenty of room to stretch out and relax.

So why wait? Come take a test drive and experience the 2009 Chevrolet HHR LT for yourself. With its impressive performance, spacious interior, and stylish design, this car won't be on the market for long. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it your own today!

    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    • Keyfob engine start control - Get an early start. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, thanks to Keyfob engine start control.
    Powertrain and Mechanical
    • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
    • Inline-4 engines produce adequate horsepower while typically offering better fuel efficiency and more economical maintenance than larger engines.
    Technology and Telematics

description: HARD TO FIND!!! ONLY 31,200 MILES!!! LOADED!!! LANE DEPARURE WARNING!!! HEATED AND DUAL POWER SEATS!!! POWER MOONROFF!!! AND MUCH MORE!!! PLEASE HURRY!!! WILL NOT LAST LONG!!!Toyota's Highlander is one of the most well-known three-row midsize SUVs around. It's a great choice for growing families and offers versatility similar to a minivan but is more enjoyable to drive and easier to maneuver in most cases. The 2023 Highlander is based on the most recent generation Highlander that debuted in 2020 and receives some updates this year.Continue reading Edmunds Expert Rating below How does the Highlander drive? The latest Highlander has a turbocharged four-cylinder engine instead of the long-running V6. Well, color us impressed because we don't miss the V6. The four-cylinder makes plenty of torque at low rpm, and that helps make the Highlander pleasant to drive around town. At the Edmunds test track, our all-wheel-drive Highlander accelerated from 0 to 60 mph in 7.4 seconds, which is a bit quicker than most V6-equipped three-row midsize SUVs.The Highlander's ability to stop quickly and confidently as well as negotiate a twisty road is solid. Body roll is controlled as you go around turns, and the available torque-vectoring AWD system also helps by applying engine power to individual rear wheels to subtly enhance the SUV's handling balance. (It also has the usual benefit of extra traction in slick conditions.) All of this advanced technology helps the Highlander feel more nimble than the average midsize SUV. Overall, the Highlander makes daily driving a low-effort activity, which is most important.

description:
Discover unmatched choice at Westgate Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram in Raleigh, home to a huge lineup of new vehicles and one of the largest used-car inventories on the east coast with 1,000+ options ready to drive.

This 2017 Ford Explorer XLT offers an impressive array of premium features that elevate your driving experience:

• Comfort Package
• Driver Connect Package
• Equipment Group 202A
• XLT Technology Feature Bundle

Indulge in the convenience of SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System, Dual-Zone Electronic Automatic Temperature Control, and the Forward Sensing System. Stay connected with the Voice-Activated Touchscreen Navigation System and enjoy the added security of BLIS Blind Spot Information System and the Auto-Dimming Driver's Sideview Mirror. The Remote Start System and Hands-Free Foot-Activated Liftgate add exceptional functionality, while the 2 Driver Configurable 4.2" Color LCD Displays, Auto-Dimming Rear-View Mirror, Heated Steering Wheel, and Leather Heated Bucket Seats provide unparalleled comfort.

This Explorer's powerful 3.5L 6-Cylinder engine, paired with a 6-Speed Automatic Transmission, delivers an impressive balance of performance and efficiency, with EPA-estimated fuel economy ratings of 17 MPG in the city and 24 MPG on the highway. The sleek White exterior, complemented by the 20" Polished Aluminum Wheels, creates a bold and sophisticated appearance that is sure to turn heads.

Boasting a well-equipped interior and a wealth of advanced features, this 2017 Ford Explorer XLT is the perfect blend of capability, technology, and style. Why BUY from Moses Factory Outlet? When you choose this Graphite Grey Metallic 2023 Mercedes-Benz E-Class E 450 with 17,992 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! What this vehicle includes: Exterior Lighting Package ($750 value)
  • LED Intelligent Light System
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

The 2023 Ford Bronco Wildtrak in Eruption Green Metallic captures the spirit of adventure and rugged style, perfect for those with an adventurous heart. Driven by a powerful 2.7L EcoBoost V6 engine paired with a smooth 10-speed automatic transmission, this 4WD icon is built to tackle terrains from urban streets to rocky trails with ease.

Step into the luxurious Black Onyx interior where functionality meets comfort. Heated leather-trimmed seats offer warmth on chilly mornings, while the dual-zone automatic temperature control ensures you and your passengers travel comfortably in any weather. The tilting and telescoping steering wheel allows you to find the perfect driving position, enhancing your journey's enjoyment.

Stay connected and entertained with the advanced technology suite. The 12" LCD touchscreen with SYNC 4 offers seamless smartphone integration and an intuitive user experience. With the Connected Navigation system, finding your next destination is as effortless as navigating city traffic with confidence, backed by a suite of sensors and a high-resolution 360-degree camera.

Safety takes center stage with this Bronco, incorporating a robust set of features that include dual front impact airbags, side impact airbags, and an emergency communication system. Equipped with integrated roll-over protection and electronic stability control, you can feel secure knowing that this vehicle is designed to keep you protected, regardless of the journey.

Whether its city commuting or weekend camping trips, the Bronco Wildtrak is your perfect match. Its robust suspension and additional sound deadening make it a serene escape, no matter where the road takes you. The standout Eruption Green Metallic paint adds a unique flair to this versatile SUV, making it a head-turner wherever you go.

At Newton Chevrolet GMC, we believe in offering the very best to our customers, ensuring their experiences match the caliber of our vehicles. The 2023 Ford Bronco Wildtrak is more than just a vehicle, it's your passport to adventure. Visit us today for a test drive and let us help you make it yours!
