description: Vehicle Highlights:Personal vehicleExtensive vehicle service history2.0L Boxer 4-cylinder engine (148 hp, 145 lb-ft torque)Symmetrical all-wheel drive15-inch steel wheels with covers6.2-inch touchscreen infotainment systemAM/FM/CD player with 4 speakersBluetooth hands-free phone and audio streamingUSB port and auxiliary inputPower windows and door locksKeyless entryCloth upholsteryRearview cameraTilt-and-telescoping steering wheelAir conditioning60/40 split-folding rear seatsVehicle dynamics control (stability and traction control)Anti-lock braking system (ABS)Front, side, and curtain airbagsTire pressure monitoring systemThe 2016 Subaru Impreza 2.0i is a standout in the compact car segment thanks to its standard all-wheel-drive system, practical interior, and strong reputation for safety and reliability. As the entry-level trim in the Impreza lineup, the 2.0i offers a no-frills approach to daily transportation but still includes the essential features modern drivers expect. Available in both sedan and hatchback body styles, it appeals to budget-conscious buyers who want a capable vehicle that performs well in all weather conditions.Under the hood, the 2016 Impreza 2.0i is powered by a 2.0-liter horizontally opposed (Boxer) 4-cylinder engine producing 148 horsepower and 145 lb-ft of torque. While not a performance powerhouse, the engine provides adequate acceleration for city and highway driving. It comes standard with a 5-speed manual transmission, while a CVT (continuously variable transmission) is available and more commonly found. The key advantage of the Impreza is its symmetrical all-wheel drive, which delivers enhanced grip and stability, especially in wet or snowy conditions—a rare feature in this segment and a major selling point.The interior is functional and well-organized, with straightforward controls and good outward visibility. While materials are more utilitarian than upscale, build quality is solid. The cabin offers ample headroom and legroom for both front and rear passengers, and the hatchback version adds even more cargo versatility. Ride comfort is commendable, with a suspension tuned more for comfort than sportiness, making it a smooth and quiet companion for commuting or longer trips.In terms of technology and features, the base 2.0i trim includes a decent range of equipment for the price. The standard touchscreen infotainment system is easy to use and includes Bluetooth connectivity and smartphone integration via USB. Subaru focused heavily on safety with the 2016 model, and even the base trim benefits from its strong safety ratings and stable handling. Though it lacks some of the upscale features and finishes found in higher trims, the 2.0i delivers exceptional value for those prioritizing safety, capability, and all-weather performance. description:
Discover the ultimate driving experience with this stunning 2023 Porsche Cayenne Platinum Edition. Boasting a captivating blue exterior and a meticulously crafted interior, this SUV is a true testament to Porsche's unparalleled engineering and design.

• Premium Package Plus
• 4-Zone Climate Control
• Heated Front & Rear Seats
• Soft Close Doors
• 14-Way Power Seats w/Comfort Memory
• Lane Change Assist (LCA)
• Surround View
• Front Seat Ventilation
• Trailer Hitch w/o Tow Ball

Powered by a 3.0L V6 engine and an 8-Speed Automatic with Tiptronic transmission, this Cayenne delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, with an impressive 19 MPG in the city and 23 MPG on the highway. The advanced all-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling and control, no matter the road conditions.

Indulge in the latest technology and convenience features, including a state-of-the-art navigation system, a premium 14-speaker audio system, and Porsche Communication Management. The panoramic sunroof and power liftgate add to the Cayenne's versatility, while the adaptive suspension and 21-inch alloy wheels provide a smooth, responsive ride.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and this Cayenne is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance features, including lane change assist, surround-view cameras, and a host of airbags to protect you and your passengers.

With a clean CARFAX history and our 6-month/6,000-mile powertrain warranty, you can drive with confidence, knowing that this Cayenne has been meticulously maintained and is ready to provide you with years of exceptional performance and luxury.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to experience the pinnacle of SUV engineering and design. Schedule a test drive today and discover the true power and refinement of the 2023 Porsche Cayenne Platinum Edition.

description:
Discover unmatched choice at Westgate Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram in Raleigh, home to a huge lineup of new vehicles and one of the largest used-car inventories on the east coast with 1,000+ options ready to drive.

This 2021 Chevrolet Suburban LT offers an impressive array of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Highlights include:

• LT Signature Package with 20-inch wheels, panoramic sunroof, and Max Trailering Package
• Luxury Package with advanced safety and convenience technologies
• Texas Edition with exclusive badging

Beyond the standout style, this Suburban delivers exceptional capability. The powerful EcoTec3 V8 engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission, provides ample power for towing, hauling, and navigating with confidence. Rear-wheel drive and an advanced trailering system make this Suburban a versatile choice for your active lifestyle.

Inside, premium materials and thoughtful design create a refined, spacious cabin. Heated front and second-row seats, a heated steering wheel, and a Bose premium audio system ensure everyone onboard enjoys a comfortable, well-appointed journey. The dual-pane panoramic sunroof floods the cabin with natural light, while the hands-free power liftgate and 60/40 power-folding third-row seat simplify loading and unloading.

Safety and technology are also top priorities, with features like lane keep assist, rear cross-traffic alert, and a surround-view camera system providing added peace of mind. The Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Plus system with a large touchscreen display, wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, and SiriusXM with 360L keep you connected and entertained.

With its impressive capabilities, premium amenities, and advanced safety technologies, this 2021 Chevrolet Suburban LT is an exceptional choice for discerning buyers. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive at Westgate Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram in Raleigh.

Choose Westgate Chrysler Jeep Dodge Ram in Raleigh, NC for a dealership experience built on transparency, value, and customer-first service. With a wide selection of new CJDR models and an extensive inventory of quality used cars, trucks, and SUVs, Westgate is a trusted destination for shoppers across Raleigh, Durham, the Triangle and all of North Carolina.

Every vehicle at Westgate comes pre-installed with Recovr vehicle location technology and professional window tint, included for a total cost of $799.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

Discover the Versatility and Capability of the 2022 Ford F-150 XLT

This 2022 Ford F-150 XLT is a true workhorse, offering impressive capabilities and a wealth of premium features. Under the hood, the potent 2.7L V6 EcoBoost engine delivers exceptional power and efficiency, with a best-in-class towing capacity of 7,700 lbs. The 10-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive system ensure seamless, confident performance on any terrain.

The XLT trim level elevates the F-150 experience with the Equipment Group 302A High package, which includes a host of premium amenities. Enjoy the convenience of Intelligent Access with push-button start, the versatility of the power-sliding rear window, and the expansive views afforded by the twin-panel moonroof. The XLT Chrome Appearance and Sport Appearance packages add a touch of style with chrome accents, body-color bumpers, and unique wheel designs.

Inside, the F-150 XLT pampers you with dual-zone automatic climate control, 10-way power-adjustable front seats, and the advanced SYNC 4 infotainment system with a 12-inch touchscreen. The 8-inch productivity screen in the instrument cluster puts vital vehicle information at your fingertips, while the 400-watt onboard outlet provides ample power for your tools and accessories.

Whether you're tackling tough jobs or embarking on weekend adventures, this 2022 Ford F-150 XLT is ready to take on the challenge. Experience the perfect blend of capability, convenience, and style. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional truck can elevate your driving experience.

description: Our 2025 Subaru Ascent Limited AWD in Ice Silver Metallic is smartly prepared for premium family adventures! Motivated by a TurboCharged 2.4 Liter BOXER 4 Cylinder offering 260hp to a paddle-shifted CVT with standard X-MODE for extreme conditions. This All Wheel Drive SUV also takes on everyday travel in style, thanks to a responsive suspension, and it scores nearly 25mpg on the highway while showing off a bold design. Our Ascent rises above the crowd with a panoramic sunroof, adaptive LED headlights, fog lamps, 20-inch alloy wheels, a power liftgate, raised roof rails, and Crystal Black Silica mirror caps.More family-friendly details highlight our Limited cabin, where you and your crew can enjoy room for seven with heated leather power front seats, heated second-row captain's chairs, a flexible third row, a heated leather steering wheel, tri-zone automatic climate control, and plenty of cargo space. An 11.6-inch touchscreen is command central for infotainment and supports full-color navigation, WiFi compatibility, Apple CarPlay®, Android Auto®, Bluetooth®, and a Harman Kardon sound system.Subaru's advanced driver assistance systems include automatic braking, blind-spot monitoring, adaptive cruise control, lane-departure warning, a rearview camera, rear cross-traffic alert, forward collision warning, and a driver attention monitor. Climb aboard our Ascent Limited, and keep on going! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Subaru of Loveland Test Drive Towards Ownership!At Subaru of Loveland we pride ourselves on our exceptional customer experience and being a business that has been family owned and operated since 1960. We appreciate each and every individual that we have the pleasure of doing business with, and that's why we offer a number of discounts and deals to every customer who purchases a vehicle from Subaru of Loveland.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with the 2025 Ford Mustang Mach-E Premium. This all-electric marvel combines the iconic Mustang styling with cutting-edge technology and uncompromising performance.

Boasting a host of premium features, this Mustang Mach-E stands out from the crowd. Key highlights include:

• Detailed inside and out
• Molten Magenta Metallic Tinted Clearcoat exterior
• Mobile Power Cord (120V/240V) for convenient charging
• Connected Navigation system for seamless exploration
• 10-speaker B&O Sound System for an immersive audio experience

The Mustang Mach-E Premium also comes equipped with the Equipment Group 300A Standard Package, ensuring you enjoy a comprehensive suite of advanced technologies and creature comforts.

This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and is in exceptional condition, with just 11 miles on the odometer. Certified pre-owned, it has undergone a rigorous inspection and reconditioning process to meet the highest standards of quality and reliability.

Imagine the thrill of commanding a Mustang Mach-E with its powerful electric motor and rear-wheel-drive performance. With an impressive EPA-estimated 106 MPGe in the city and 98 MPGe on the highway, this Mustang Mach-E delivers an unparalleled blend of efficiency and exhilaration.

The spacious and well-appointed interior of the Mustang Mach-E Premium offers a premium driving experience. Sink into the heated and ventilated ActiveX bucket seats, enjoy the convenience of the power liftgate, and let the 360L SiriusXM audio system transport you.

Safety is paramount, and the Mustang Mach-E Premium is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including 911 Assist, Rear Parking Camera, and Electronic Stability Control.

This exceptional Mustang Mach-E Premium is a rare find, and we invite you to experience its remarkable capabilities firsthand. Schedule a test drive today and discover the future of electric performance.

description:
The 2023 Toyota bZ4X XLE FWD stands out as a practical and well-balanced entry into Toyotas all-electric lineup. On the road, it delivers a smooth, quiet ride that feels refined and easy to live with, especially for daily commuting. The front-wheel-drive setup keeps handling predictable and efficient, while the electric powertrain provides instant torque for confident acceleration around town.

Inside, the XLE trim offers a comfortable and thoughtfully designed cabin with supportive seating and a modern layout. The infotainment system is intuitive, with smartphone integration that works seamlessly, and the interior space is generous enough to accommodate passengers and cargo without feeling cramped. Toyotas safety technology is a strong point, adding an extra layer of confidence whether driving in traffic or on longer trips.

Overall, the 2023 bZ4X XLE FWD feels like a smart, user-friendly electric SUV that focuses on comfort, reliability, and low operating costs rather than flash. For buyers looking to transition into an electric vehicle backed by Toyotas reputation for dependability, this bZ4X XLE represents a solid and sensible option that is well suited for everyday use.

Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

description: Vehicle Highlights:No accidents reportedPersonal vehicleExtensive vehicle service history2.5L 4-cylinder BOXER engine (175 hp, 174 lb-ft)Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT)Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive Leather-trimmed upholsteryHeated front and rear seats10-way power driver's seat with memory4-way power passenger seatDual-zone automatic climate control7-inch touchscreen infotainment systemNavigation and smartphone integrationHarman Kardon 12-speaker premium audio system Blind-spot detection with rear cross-traffic alertRearview cameraAdaptive cruise controlPre-collision brakingLane departure and sway warningLane keep assistPower rear liftgateRoof rails with integrated crossbars18-inch alloy wheelsFog lightsThe 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited remains one of the most versatile and well-rounded vehicles in the midsize crossover segment. It offers the ruggedness of an SUV with the comfort and drivability of a car, thanks to its raised ground clearance and standard all-wheel drive. In the Limited trim, the Outback leans further into refinement, delivering a premium interior, a quiet cabin, and a host of technology and safety features that enhance both convenience and peace of mind.Powering the 2.5i Limited is a 2.5-liter four-cylinder engine producing 175 horsepower and 174 lb-ft of torque, mated to a continuously variable transmission (CVT). While not the fastest in its class, the powertrain provides adequate acceleration and shines in fuel efficiency, with EPA ratings of up to 25 mpg city and 32 mpg highway. Subaru’s symmetrical all-wheel drive system ensures confident traction in various road conditions, whether navigating snowy streets or gravel trails. The Outback’s ride is composed and comfortable, with responsive steering and a suspension setup that absorbs road imperfections with ease.Inside, the 2.5i Limited offers a surprisingly upscale experience. The cabin features high-quality materials, including leather-trimmed upholstery and soft-touch surfaces. Both front and rear passengers benefit from spacious, supportive seating, and the heated rear seats add a welcome touch of luxury for those in the back. The power-adjustable front seats, with driver-side memory settings, provide excellent comfort for longer drives. Subaru also equipped this trim with an upgraded infotainment system featuring a 7-inch touchscreen, navigation, Bluetooth, HD Radio, and smartphone integration. The system is user-friendly, and the available Harman Kardon premium audio system provides rich sound quality.Safety is another strong suit for the 2017 Outback 2.5i Limited. Subaru’s EyeSight Driver Assist Technology was available as an option and includes adaptive cruise control, pre-collision braking, lane departure warning, and lane keep assist. Even without EyeSight, the Limited trim includes blind-spot detection with rear cross-traffic alert and a rearview camera as standard, making it one of the safest choices in its class.Practicality is where the Outback continues to dominate. Its wagon-like body provides ample interior room and exceptional cargo capacity—up to 73.3 cubic feet with the rear seats folded. The wide-opening rear hatch and low load floor make it easy to haul gear, groceries, or luggage, and the standard roof rails with integrated crossbars add to its utility.Overall, the 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited is an excellent all-purpose vehicle for drivers who need comfort, capability, and safety in one smartly designed package. It combines everyday usability with rugged confidence and a touch of luxury, making it a perennial favorite among active families and outdoor enthusiasts alike. description:
Experience flagship luxury and uncompromising performance with this one-owner, Clean CARFAX, Green Metallic 2024 BMW X7 M60i AWD, an exceptional full-size luxury SUV that blends commanding V8 power with advanced technology and first-class comfort. Powered by a thrilling 4.4L twin-turbocharged V8 paired to an 8-speed automatic sport transmission and BMWs intelligent all-wheel drive system, the X7 M60i delivers effortless acceleration, confident handling, and a refined ride thanks to its adaptive suspension and auto-leveling system.

This X7 is equipped with the highly desirable Executive Package, featuring indulgent front massaging multi-contour seats, premium glass interior controls, heated and cooled cup holders, and the stunning panoramic Sky Lounge LED roof that transforms the cabin with ambient lighting. The M Sport Package Pro and M Sport Professional Package enhance both style and performance with aggressive exterior accents, extended Shadowline trim, sport steering wheel, carbon fiber interior trim, and M Sport brakes with black calipers, all riding on striking 22-inch double-spoke wheels that complete its commanding stance.

Inside, the cabin is trimmed in Extended Merino leather upholstery and offers exceptional comfort for all passengers with heated and ventilated front seats, front and rear heated seats, a heated steering wheel, and advanced 5-zone automatic climate control. The three-row configuration provides spacious seating with a power-reclining third row, making this SUV equally suited for family travel or executive driving.

Technology is equally impressive, highlighted by BMW Live Cockpit Pro with a full digital display, head-up display, gesture control, BMW Maps navigation, wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, personal eSIM 5G connectivity, and a wireless charging device. Audiophiles will appreciate the immersive harman/kardon surround sound system, while safety and convenience are enhanced by a rearview camera, rain-sensing wipers, speed-sensitive steering, advanced stability and traction control systems, and BMW Assist eCall emergency communication.

With an odometer reading 18,664 miles below market average, this 2024 BMW X7 M60i represents a rare opportunity to own a meticulously equipped luxury SUV that delivers power, presence, and prestige in one remarkable package.

We offer market-based pricing and encourage you to call to confirm availability. We will buy your vehicle even if you dont purchase ours. Open 7 days a week, we invite you to visit our new state-of-the-art facility and experience our award-winning customer service firsthand.

description:
2022 Land Rover Defender 90 X-Dynamic S is a Modern Icon, Pure Capability

If you're looking for a luxury SUV that blends heritage, off-road dominance, and everyday comfort, this 2022 Land Rover Defender 90 X-Dynamic S delivers in every category. Bold, refined, and engineered to conquer virtually any terrain, its the perfect balance between rugged adventure and premium sophistication.

Design & Presence

The Defender 90 stands out instantly with its short wheelbase, muscular stance, and unmistakable silhouette. Finished in a stunning exterior color that highlights its modern yet classic design, the X-Dynamic S trim adds distinctive gloss black accents, rugged body cladding, and signature LED lighting.

Compact in size but bold in personality, the 2-door configuration gives it a sportier, more agile feel compared to the 4-door 110, making it ideal for city driving while still ready for the trail.

Performance & Capability

Under the hood, the Defender 90 X-Dynamic S offers confident, smooth power delivery paired with Land Rovers legendary all-wheel-drive system. Whether cruising highways or navigating rough terrain, it remains composed, capable, and impressively refined.

With Terrain Response, advanced traction management, and exceptional ground clearance, this Defender doesn't just look the part it performs.

Interior & Technology

Inside, the Defender blends durability with luxury. Premium materials, supportive seating, and a modern digital layout create a cabin that feels both upscale and functional.

Features may include:

Pivi Pro infotainment system

Large touchscreen display

Apple CarPlay & Android Auto

Meridian premium sound system

Dual-zone climate control

Advanced driver assistance features

The Defender's interior is designed to be practical yet stylish, with clever storage solutions and a commanding driving position.

Driving Experience

On the road, the Defender 90 feels planted and confident. The shorter wheelbase makes it surprisingly nimble, while still offering a smooth, composed ride. Its equally at home commuting through town or heading off-grid for weekend adventures.

Why This Defender?

Iconic design with modern refinement
Highly capable off-road performance
Premium technology and safety features
Rare 2-door configuration
Excellent condition and well maintained

This 2022 Defender 90 X-Dynamic S represents a unique opportunity to own one of the most sought-after modern SUVs on the market.

description:
Introducing the sleek and stylish 2010 Nissan Altima 2.5 S! This impressive sedan is the perfect combination of elegance and performance. Step inside and experience the spacious and comfortable interior, with plenty of legroom for all passengers. The 2.5-liter engine packs a punch and delivers an impressive fuel efficiency of 32 MPG on the highway. With only X miles on the odometer, this Altima is in pristine condition and ready to take you on countless adventures.

Equipped with features such as power windows, remote keyless entry, and a premium audio system, this Altima offers convenience and luxury at an affordable price. The 16-inch alloy wheels and chrome accents add a touch of sophistication to the exterior, making heads turn wherever you go. Plus, the spacious trunk allows for ample storage space, perfect for road trips or daily errands.

Safety is a top priority with the Altima, as it comes equipped with airbags, electronic stability control, and anti-lock brakes. With its solid construction and advanced safety features, you can drive with peace of mind knowing that you and your passengers are well-protected.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this 2010 Nissan Altima 2.5 S. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and experience the ultimate combination of style, performance, and affordability. Hurry, this Altima won't stay on our lot for long!

Quick Order Package 27W Rebel
    Comfort
    • Heated steering wheel - A warm touch. Trying to drive with bulky winter gloves on isn't always easy. Keep your hands warm in cold temperatures so you can ditch the mitts and get a firm grip with this heated steering wheel.
    Convenience
    • Keyfob engine start control - Get an early start. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, thanks to Keyfob engine start control.
    Safety and Security
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.

description: The 2023 Ford Transit350 XLT in Oxford White is a one owner passenger van designed for capacity, visibility, and everyday practicality. With seating for up to 15, plus split bench 3rdrow seating and a 4throw bench, its built to move groups comfortably and efficiently. The 3.5L V6 Flex Fuel engine delivers dependable power, while the 360degree camera with split view and reverse sensing system provide excellent visibility when maneuvering in tight areas. Auto high beam headlights, front fog lamps, and the honeycomb mesh grille with chrome surround add both function and style. For organizations, families, or transport needs, this Transit350 XLT offers space, confidence, and a clean ownership history in one well equipped package.**ONE OWNER**, 15-Passenger Seats, 360-Degree Camera w/Split View, 3rd row seats: split-bench, 4th-Row Bench Seat, Auto High-beam Headlights, Front Fog Lamps, Honeycomb Mesh Grille w/Chrome Surround, Reverse Sensing System.Our customers tell us the most unpleasant aspect of buying an used vehicle is negotiating the price. With that in mind, we've decided to give everyone our best price right up front. We have our best price in every vehicle at all times. We have priced our vehicles at the true best price to assure the integrity and fairness of your car buying experience. This is accomplished through weekly market comparison surveys. One price, the same price, every day, for all customers. In other words, we price the car ... not the customer. We're in Minot ND, also serving Bismarck, Williston, Dickinson, Devils Lake, and Fargo.

description:
Why BUY from Hyundai of Union County? When you choose this Magnetic Gray Metallic 2016 Toyota 4Runner SR5 Premium with 88,222 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! One Owner! What this vehicle includes: Premium Package with Softex
  • Auto-Dimming Rearview Mirror
  • Softex Synthetic Leather Seat Trim
  • Body Color Heated Mirrors
  • Garage Door Opener
  • Power Tilt and Slide Moonroof with Sunshade
  • Entune Premium Audio with Navigation
Comfort
  • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.
MAGNETIC GRAY METALLIC Come on in to Hyundai of Union County today at 3220 W Highway 74 Monroe NC 28110 or call 9805258560 to schedule a test drive! All advertised prices excludes government fees, taxes, installed accessories, CPO costs and dealer recon.

description: Experience capability and comfort in this stylish White 2024 Jeep Compass Limited 4x4 SUV. Powered by a 2.0L Turbo I4 engine with an 8-speed automatic transmission, this Compass is ready for city driving or weekend adventures. The Limited trim features premium leatherette bucket seats, heated front seats, and a heated steering wheel for year-round comfort. Stay connected with a 10.1-inch Uconnect touchscreen, wireless Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, Amazon Alexa compatibility, and integrated Wi-Fi hotspot. Advanced safety tech includes adaptive cruise control, lane keeping assist, blind spot monitoring, front & rear cross traffic alerts, and front automatic emergency braking with pedestrian detection. Enjoy convenience features like remote start, push-button start, power-adjustable driver's seat, rain-sensing wipers, rearview camera, and rear parking sensors. Bold exterior touches-LED headlights, chrome window trim, and black roof rails-complete the look. This Compass delivers Jeep's legendary 4x4 performance, modern tech, and everyday comfort in one well-equipped package. Visit us to test drive and discover the perfect blend of adventure and sophistication.

description:
Discover the ultimate off-road companion in the 2019 Jeep Renegade Trailhawk. This rugged and capable SUV is ready to take you on adventures beyond the beaten path, with its impressive 4WD system and a host of advanced features that will elevate your driving experience.

Boasting a bold and distinctive exterior in a sleek Silver color, the Renegade Trailhawk stands out from the crowd. Its impressive list of features includes:

• Dual-Pane Panoramic Power Sunroof
• Safety and Security Group (Security Alarm, Blind Spot & Cross Path Detection, Tonneau Cover)
• Popular Equipment Group (Power Adjust 8-Way Driver Seat, 40/20/40 Rear Seat with Trunk Pass-Thru, Rear View Auto Dim Mirror, Power 4-Way Driver Lumbar Adjust)
• Passive Entry Remote Start Package (Keyless Entry with Panic Alarm, Remote Start System)

This Renegade Trailhawk is powered by a 1.3L I4 engine mated to a 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission, delivering a impressive 22 city/27 highway MPG. With its 177HP power rating, this Jeep offers the perfect balance of performance and efficiency, ensuring you can tackle any terrain with confidence.

Beyond its impressive capabilities, the Renegade Trailhawk pampers you with a host of premium features, including Uconnect 4 with 7" Display, Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control, and a Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel. The spacious and versatile interior, with its 40/20/40 Rear Seat with Trunk Pass-Thru, allows you to accommodate all your cargo and passenger needs.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Blind Spot & Cross Path Detection, ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera, and a comprehensive suite of airbags to keep you and your loved ones secure on the road.

Whether you're seeking a capable off-road companion or a stylish and well-appointed daily driver, the 2019 Jeep Renegade Trailhawk is the perfect choice. Experience the thrill of the open road and the freedom to explore with this exceptional SUV. Visit our showroom today to take it for a test drive and discover why the Renegade Trailhawk is the perfect fit for your adventurous lifestyle.
